description: Elos Medtech AB engages in the development and manufacture of medical technology products and components. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 531 full-time employees.  The firm is engaged in the development, manufacturing and sale of medical technology products and components, with focus on dental and orthopedic implants and instruments. The firm's products include implants, prosthetics, digital dentistry, screws, drills, plates, pins and wires, as well as other metal instruments, and injection molded disposable plastics, such as caps, tubes, vials, dishes and fittings for high-performance liquid chromatography (HPCL) used in diagnostics. The firm offers also customized turnkey solutions. The company has operating facilities in Sweden, Denmark, China and the United States, and distributes its products worldwide.
name: Elos Medtech AB
